ext:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">446</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T25">VI</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">, t. CCXII, p. 19-a. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">447</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/><text:tab/>é<text:tab/>dit. M.-M. Davy, p. 108.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">448</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T26">Charitas</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">, mot que Pierre de Blois est un peu étonné de rencontrer chez Cicéron et qu’il lui reproche de ne pas bien comprendre.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">449</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T26">Ibid</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">., p. 122.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">450</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/>Ibid., p. 512-514. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">451</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/>Cf., p. 526, les sources diverses de l’affection.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">452</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/>P. 492. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">453</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T26">Ibid</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">., p. 562.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T27">454</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24"> <text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T25">VI</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">, t. CLXXXVI, 639-1010 ; cf. R.-M. Martin, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T25">CXIV</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">, t. I : </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T26">Quaestiones de divina pagina</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T24">, Louvain, 1932.</text:span><text:span te